const colors = {
  snow: '#f1f1f1',
  white: '#ffffff',
  black: '#000000',
  softBlack: '#0c0c0c',
  lightGrey: '#dfe6e9',
  grey: '#95a5a6',
  darkGrey: '#2c3e50',
  green: '#4ecdc4',
  red: '#fc5c65',
  danger: '#ff5252',
  yellow: '#ffe66d',
}

export const palette = {
  primary: colors.green,
  secondary: colors.red,
  danger: colors.danger,
  alert: colors.yellow,
  text: colors.softBlack,

  black: colors.black,
  white: colors.white,
  snow: colors.snow,
  lightGrey: colors.lightGrey,
  grey: colors.grey,
  darkGrey: colors.darkGrey,
}
